OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBreezy with the chance of
OL,6,Fshowers in the west at first.
OL,7,FOtherwise, dry with sunny spells
OL,8,Fthough cloud increasing from the
OL,9,Fsouthwest later. Winds easing through
OL,10,Fthe day, feeling warm in sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry and mostly cloudy,
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain spreading northeast.
OL,14,FRain clears during the early hours to
OL,15,Fleave clear spells and the odd
OL,16,Fisolated shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
